{"id":33,"date":"2017-12-18T10:16:56","date_gmt":"2017-12-18T10:16:56","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/localhost\/wordpress\/?page_id=33"},"modified":"2020-10-19T18:53:00","modified_gmt":"2020-10-19T12:53:00","slug":"profile","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/profile\/","title":{"rendered":"Profile"},"content":{"rendered":"<div id=\"pl-33\"  class=\"panel-layout\" ><div id=\"pg-33-0\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-has-style\" ><div class=\"siteorigin-panels-stretch panel-row-style panel-row-style-for-33-0\" style=\"padding: 100px 0; \" data-stretch-type=\"full\" data-overlay=\"true\" data-overlay-color=\"#000000\" ><div id=\"pgc-33-0-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\" ><div id=\"panel-33-0-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sydney_skills sydney_skills_widget panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"0\" ><div style=\"text-align: center;\" data-title-color=\"#443f3f\" data-headings-color=\"#443f3f\" class=\"panel-widget-style panel-widget-style-for-33-0-0-0\" >\r\n\t\t<h3 class=\"widget-title\">Successfulness<\/h3>\r\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"roll-progress\">\r\n \t\t\t<div class=\"name\">Designing<\/div>\r\n\t\t\t<div class=\"perc\">80%<\/div>\r\n            <div class=\"progress-bar\" data-percent=\"80\" data-waypoint-active=\"yes\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"progress-animate\"><\/div>\r\n\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t   \r\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"roll-progress\">\r\n \t\t\t<div class=\"name\">Quality Control<\/div>\r\n\t\t\t<div class=\"perc\">85%<\/div>\r\n            <div class=\"progress-bar\" data-percent=\"85\" data-waypoint-active=\"yes\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"progress-animate\"><\/div>\r\n\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t \r\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"roll-progress\">\r\n \t\t\t<div class=\"name\">Merchandising<\/div>\r\n\t\t\t<div class=\"perc\">90%<\/div>\r\n            <div class=\"progress-bar\" data-percent=\"90\" data-waypoint-active=\"yes\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"progress-animate\"><\/div>\r\n\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t \r\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"roll-progress\">\r\n \t\t\t<div class=\"name\">Production<\/div>\r\n\t\t\t<div class=\"perc\">95%<\/div>\r\n            <div class=\"progress-bar\" data-percent=\"95\" data-waypoint-active=\"yes\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"progress-animate\"><\/div>\r\n\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t \r\n\r\n\t<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><div id=\"pg-33-1\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-has-style\" ><div class=\"siteorigin-panels-stretch panel-row-style panel-row-style-for-33-1\" style=\"background-image: url(https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Office.jpg);padding: 100px 0; \" data-stretch-type=\"full-stretched\" data-hasbg=\"hasbg\" data-overlay=\"true\" data-overlay-color=\"#000000\" ><div id=\"pgc-33-1-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\" ><div id=\"panel-33-1-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_text panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"1\" ><div style=\"text-align: center;\" data-title-color=\"#443f3f\" data-headings-color=\"#ffffff\" class=\"panel-widget-style panel-widget-style-for-33-1-0-0\" >\t\t\t<div class=\"textwidget\"><h4>At JDK Group,<\/h4>\n<h5>we bridge the world with Bangladesh. Since 2009 we have been working in the RMG industry catering for our many valued customers with efficiency, honesty and reliability.<\/h5>\n<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><div id=\"pg-33-2\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-has-style\" ><div class=\"siteorigin-panels-stretch panel-row-style panel-row-style-for-33-2\" style=\"padding: 25px 0; \" data-stretch-type=\"full\" data-overlay=\"true\" data-overlay-color=\"#000000\" ><div id=\"pgc-33-2-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\" ><div id=\"panel-33-2-0-0\" class=\"widget_text so-panel widget widget_custom_html panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"2\" ><div style=\"text-align: center;\" data-title-color=\"#443f3f\" data-headings-color=\"#440000\" class=\"widget_text panel-widget-style panel-widget-style-for-33-2-0-0\" ><div class=\"textwidget custom-html-widget\"><style>\n@import url('https:\/\/fonts.googleapis.com\/css?family=Cabin+Sketch:700');\n<\/style> \n<h1 style=\"font-family: 'Cabin Sketch', cursive;\">\n\tBUSINESS PORTFOLIO\n<\/h1>\n<hr><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><div id=\"pg-33-3\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-has-style\" ><div style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #1e73be;padding: 100px 0; \" data-overlay=\"true\" data-overlay-color=\"#000000\" class=\"panel-row-style panel-row-style-for-33-3\" ><div id=\"pgc-33-3-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\" ><div id=\"panel-33-3-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_text panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"3\" ><div style=\"text-align: left;\" data-title-color=\"#443f3f\" data-headings-color=\"#443f3f\" class=\"panel-widget-style panel-widget-style-for-33-3-0-0\" >\t\t\t<div class=\"textwidget\"><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Our passionate team of fashion designers, technicians, photographers creates each design line for different customers according to their individual taste and their customer range. <\/span>We convert the concepts into sketches and by choosing the trendy colors for yarn and fabric. Our Graphic team creates graphics and patterns by watercolor, pencil, photography and 3d illustrations. These sketches and colors are sent to our design sections in BD and China. We always take inspiration by attending fashion shows, fairs and shopping. We constantly update our collections with the trend. We always keep joining bellow<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>PITI UOMO<\/li>\n<li>Bread&amp;Butter<\/li>\n<li>PANORAMA, Berlin<\/li>\n<li>CPD, Dusseldorf<\/li>\n<li>Magic Show, Las Vegas<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>We also shop all over US and EUROPE and constantly follow fashion magazines and online fashion blogs. We give our best efforts to offer the exclusively customized products to our clients.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div><\/div><\/div><div id=\"pgc-33-3-1\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\" ><div id=\"panel-33-3-1-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_media_image panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"4\" ><div style=\"text-align: center;\" id=\"design\" data-title-color=\"#443f3f\" data-headings-color=\"#443f3f\" class=\"panel-widget-style panel-widget-style-for-33-3-1-0\" ><h3 class=\"widget-title\">Trendy Design<\/h3><img width=\"612\" height=\"408\" src=\"https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/544667458-612x612.jpg\" class=\"image wp-image-503  attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto;\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/544667458-612x612.jpg 612w, https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/544667458-612x612-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/544667458-612x612-230x153.jpg 230w, https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/544667458-612x612-350x233.jpg 350w, https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/544667458-612x612-480x320.jpg 480w, https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/544667458-612x612-600x400.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 612px) 100vw, 612px\" \/><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><div id=\"pg-33-4\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-has-style\" ><div style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #1e73be;background-image: url(https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/img_teaser.jpg);padding: 100px 0; \" data-hasbg=\"hasbg\" data-overlay=\"true\" data-overlay-color=\"#000000\" class=\"panel-row-style panel-row-style-for-33-4\" ><div id=\"pgc-33-4-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\" ><div id=\"panel-33-4-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_media_image panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"5\" ><div style=\"text-align: center;\" data-title-color=\"#443f3f\" data-headings-color=\"#443f3f\" class=\"panel-widget-style panel-widget-style-for-33-4-0-0\" ><img width=\"600\" height=\"400\" src=\"https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Collection-600x400.jpg\" class=\"image wp-image-95  attachment-600x400 size-600x400\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto;\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Collection-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Collection-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Collection-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Collection-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Collection-830x554.jpg 830w, https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Collection-230x153.jpg 230w, https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Collection-350x234.jpg 350w, https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Collection-480x320.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/><\/div><\/div><\/div><div id=\"pgc-33-4-1\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\" ><div id=\"panel-33-4-1-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_text panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"6\" ><div style=\"text-align: left;\" data-title-color=\"#ffffff\" data-headings-color=\"#443f3f\" class=\"panel-widget-style panel-widget-style-for-33-4-1-0\" ><h3 class=\"widget-title\">Collections<\/h3>\t\t\t<div class=\"textwidget\"><p>We strive at JDK to be ahead of time and be the trendsetter. We produce our own collections every season (AW\/ SS) with a range of styles that comprise garments for all gender and across all ages.<\/p>\n<p>Our collections are always comprises the latest\/upcoming yarn, accessories, colors and of course designs.<\/p>\n<p>We offer samples in both Manuel and Jacquard knits. We also develop samples\/designs given to us by our customers as per their requirements.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><div id=\"pg-33-5\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-has-style\" ><div style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #1e73be;padding: 100px 0; \" data-overlay=\"true\" data-overlay-color=\"#000000\" class=\"panel-row-style panel-row-style-for-33-5\" ><div id=\"pgc-33-5-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\" ><div id=\"panel-33-5-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_text panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"7\" ><div style=\"text-align: left;\" data-title-color=\"#443f3f\" data-headings-color=\"#443f3f\" class=\"panel-widget-style panel-widget-style-for-33-5-0-0\" ><h3 class=\"widget-title\">Merchandising<\/h3>\t\t\t<div class=\"textwidget\"><p>Our well-trained and capable teams of merchandisers are working around the clock to give our customers all the support they need. Starting from procurement stage of yarn, fabric, lab-dips, hand-looms, trims till the finished products are shipped.<\/p>\n<p>We have 40 stuffs in merchandising team, divided in to 5 divisions in JDK head-office to attain our valued customers and 15 merchandisers in 3 factories to give production\/development feedback.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div><\/div><\/div><div id=\"pgc-33-5-1\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\" ><div id=\"panel-33-5-1-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_media_image panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"8\" ><div style=\"text-align: center;\" id=\"merchandising\" data-title-color=\"#443f3f\" data-headings-color=\"#443f3f\" class=\"panel-widget-style panel-widget-style-for-33-5-1-0\" ><img width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" src=\"https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/collage-1024x768.jpg\" class=\"image wp-image-526  attachment-large size-large\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto;\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/collage-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/collage-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/collage-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/collage-830x623.jpg 830w, https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/collage-230x173.jpg 230w, https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/collage-350x263.jpg 350w, https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/collage-480x360.jpg 480w, https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/collage-600x450.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><div id=\"pg-33-6\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-has-style\" ><div style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #1e73be;background-image: url(https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Factory.jpg);padding: 100px 0; \" data-hasbg=\"hasbg\" data-overlay=\"true\" data-overlay-color=\"#000000\" class=\"panel-row-style panel-row-style-for-33-6\" ><div id=\"pgc-33-6-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\" ><div id=\"panel-33-6-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_media_image panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"9\" ><div style=\"text-align: center;\" data-title-color=\"#ffffff\" data-headings-color=\"#443f3f\" class=\"panel-widget-style panel-widget-style-for-33-6-0-0\" ><img width=\"1024\" height=\"559\" src=\"https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Factory-1-1024x559.jpg\" class=\"image wp-image-174  attachment-large size-large\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto;\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Factory-1-1024x559.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Factory-1-300x164.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Factory-1-600x327.jpg 600w, https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Factory-1-768x419.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Factory-1-830x453.jpg 830w, https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Factory-1-230x125.jpg 230w, https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Factory-1-350x191.jpg 350w, https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Factory-1-480x262.jpg 480w, https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Factory-1.jpg 1650w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/div><\/div><\/div><div id=\"pgc-33-6-1\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\" ><div id=\"panel-33-6-1-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_text panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"10\" ><div style=\"text-align: left;\" data-title-color=\"#443f3f\" data-headings-color=\"#443f3f\" class=\"panel-widget-style panel-widget-style-for-33-6-1-0\" >\t\t\t<div class=\"textwidget\"><p>State of the art machinery of transnational configuration is our pride. Beside this the dedication of men and women operating the machines, whose skills and expertise are devoted to match our customers\u2019 quality specifications and on time delivery of the sweaters of international stature.<\/p>\n<p>Our all units are 100% compliance and certified by reputed authorities like BSCI, SADEX, AC-CORD, OEKO-TEX, ITX, WRAP, etc. We strictly follow a NO CHILD LABOUR Policy. As well as all other Laws and regulations set by the Bangladesh Govt. such as HEALTH AND SAFETY, MEDICAL FACILITY, BUILDING STRUCTURE etc.<\/p>\n<p>Our total factory working floor is more than 160,000 Sq-ft(4 floors), with additional space for canteen and prayer hall. We have a total of 2300 sets of knitting machines compiling all Gauges from 3gg to 12gg, and 800 sets of linking ma-chines covering all gauges.<\/p>\n<p>Our approximate total production capacity is 25,000 Dzn per month comprising all gauges. out of which 15,000 Dzn in 12gg per month.<\/p>\n<div id=\"gtx-trans\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 19px; top: -10px;\">\n<div class=\"gtx-trans-icon\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><div id=\"pg-33-7\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-has-style\" ><div style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #1e73be;padding: 100px 0; \" data-overlay=\"true\" data-overlay-color=\"#000000\" class=\"panel-row-style panel-row-style-for-33-7\" ><div id=\"pgc-33-7-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\" ><div id=\"panel-33-7-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_text panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"11\" ><div style=\"text-align: left;\" data-title-color=\"#443f3f\" data-headings-color=\"#443f3f\" class=\"panel-widget-style panel-widget-style-for-33-7-0-0\" ><h3 class=\"widget-title\">Production<\/h3>\t\t\t<div class=\"textwidget\"><p>We have our own 4 sweater manufacturing factories near Dhaka. Here more then 12,000 workers are operating for last 21 years.<\/p>\n<p>With more then 500 production stuffs, our monthly export is over 700,000pcs of sweaters. All the factories are around Dhaka and always in communication with the JDK office in Baridhara DOHS. We have separate design section in each factory for production and R&amp;D.<\/p>\n<p>Apart form our own factories; we also produce in more than 15 sweater factories in Dhaka and Chittagong and 10 knit and woven factories. In total our average monthly export in sweater is around a million pieces and knit\/woven around half a million pieces.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div><\/div><\/div><div id=\"pgc-33-7-1\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\" ><div id=\"panel-33-7-1-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_media_image panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"12\" ><div style=\"text-align: center;\" id=\"production\" data-title-color=\"#443f3f\" data-headings-color=\"#443f3f\" class=\"panel-widget-style panel-widget-style-for-33-7-1-0\" ><img width=\"973\" height=\"571\" src=\"https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/factory_process_map.jpg\" class=\"image wp-image-177  attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto;\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/factory_process_map.jpg 973w, https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/factory_process_map-300x176.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/factory_process_map-600x352.jpg 600w, https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/factory_process_map-768x451.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/factory_process_map-830x487.jpg 830w, https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/factory_process_map-230x135.jpg 230w, https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/factory_process_map-350x205.jpg 350w, https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/factory_process_map-480x282.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 973px) 100vw, 973px\" \/><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><div id=\"pg-33-8\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-has-style\" ><div style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #1e73be;background-image: url(https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/qc1.jpg);padding: 100px 0; \" data-hasbg=\"hasbg\" data-overlay=\"true\" data-overlay-color=\"#000000\" class=\"panel-row-style panel-row-style-for-33-8\" ><div id=\"pgc-33-8-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\" ><div id=\"panel-33-8-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_media_image panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"13\" ><div style=\"text-align: center;\" id=\"qc\" data-title-color=\"#ffffff\" data-headings-color=\"#ffffff\" class=\"panel-widget-style panel-widget-style-for-33-8-0-0\" ><h3 class=\"widget-title\">Quality Control<\/h3><img width=\"1632\" height=\"1224\" src=\"https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/IMG_7724.jpg\" class=\"image wp-image-185  attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto;\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/IMG_7724.jpg 1632w, https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/IMG_7724-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/IMG_7724-600x450.jpg 600w, https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/IMG_7724-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/IMG_7724-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/IMG_7724-830x623.jpg 830w, https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/IMG_7724-230x173.jpg 230w, https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/IMG_7724-350x263.jpg 350w, https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/IMG_7724-480x360.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1632px) 100vw, 1632px\" \/><\/div><\/div><\/div><div id=\"pgc-33-8-1\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\" ><div id=\"panel-33-8-1-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_text panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"14\" ><div style=\"text-align: left;\" data-title-color=\"#443f3f\" data-headings-color=\"#443f3f\" class=\"panel-widget-style panel-widget-style-for-33-8-1-0\" >\t\t\t<div class=\"textwidget\"><p>Our focused and well trained QA teams are working in every key check point of the manufacturing stages to attain the customers required quality standards. Starting from sample approval to the final production stages, our QCs are always monitoring and supervising the factory people. To achieve the stiff target of attaining the high standards, we allocate individual QA teams for individual clients, working around the clock in every factory we produce at.<\/p>\n<p>These teams at the factories are centrally monitored and regulated by the QA department stationed at JDK Fashion head office on a daily basis. Consequently, our efficient quality control system has enabled us to meet the AQL standards set by the clients.<\/p>\n<p>In order to better ourselves, we have developed a chain of procedures to ensure our required standards are met to maximize production and minimize wastage. And this also ensures on time shipment according to plan.<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Understanding the customers\u2019 quality requirements.<\/li>\n<li>Organizing &amp; training quality control department.<\/li>\n<li>Ensuring proper flow of quality requirements to the QC department.<\/li>\n<li>Ensuring proper flow of quality requirements to the Production Department.<\/li>\n<li>Establishing quality plans, parameters, inspection systems, frequency, sampling techniques etc.<\/li>\n<li>Inspection, testing, measurements as per plan.<\/li>\n<li>Record deviations<\/li>\n<li>Feedback to Production Department.<\/li>\n<li>Plan for further improvement.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>We push ourselves to the limit to make sure that the chain of procedures mentioned above are followed every time for every order.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><div id=\"pg-33-9\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-has-style\" ><div style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #1e73be;padding: 100px 0; \" data-overlay=\"true\" data-overlay-color=\"#000000\" class=\"panel-row-style panel-row-style-for-33-9\" ><div id=\"pgc-33-9-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\" ><div id=\"panel-33-9-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_text panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"15\" ><div style=\"text-align: left;\" data-title-color=\"#443f3f\" data-headings-color=\"#443f3f\" class=\"panel-widget-style panel-widget-style-for-33-9-0-0\" ><h3 class=\"widget-title\">Business Ethics &#038; Compliance<\/h3>\t\t\t<div class=\"textwidget\"><p>Our prime objective is to build a transparent bridge between our customers and us for building and maintaining a long-term relationship.<\/p>\n<p>All three of our own manufacturing units are 100% compliance. We are certified by globally recognized Auditing Companies. Over the time we have accumulated BSCI, SEDEX, WRAP, ACORD, OEKO-TEX, ITX, WALMART etc.<\/p>\n<p>We have internal compliance teams stationed in each of our factories, up keeping the compliance standards mentioned above regularly. These teams report directly to our central Compliance Department stationed in JDK head office.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div><\/div><\/div><div id=\"pgc-33-9-1\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\" ><div id=\"panel-33-9-1-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_media_image panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"16\" ><div style=\"text-align: center;\" id=\"compliance\" data-title-color=\"#443f3f\" data-headings-color=\"#443f3f\" class=\"panel-widget-style panel-widget-style-for-33-9-1-0\" ><img width=\"638\" height=\"359\" src=\"https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Compliance.jpg\" class=\"image wp-image-188  attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto;\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Compliance.jpg 638w, https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Compliance-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Compliance-600x338.jpg 600w, https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Compliance-230x129.jpg 230w, https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Compliance-350x197.jpg 350w, https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Compliance-480x270.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 638px) 100vw, 638px\" \/><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><div id=\"pg-33-10\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-has-style\" ><div style=\"background-image: url(https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/commercial.png);padding: 100px 0; \" data-hasbg=\"hasbg\" data-overlay=\"true\" data-overlay-color=\"#000000\" class=\"panel-row-style panel-row-style-for-33-10\" ><div id=\"pgc-33-10-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\" ><div id=\"panel-33-10-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_media_image panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"17\" ><div style=\"text-align: center;\" data-title-color=\"#ffffff\" data-headings-color=\"#443f3f\" class=\"panel-widget-style panel-widget-style-for-33-10-0-0\" ><h3 class=\"widget-title\">Commercial Team<\/h3><a href=\"https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Commerce.jpg\"><img width=\"300\" height=\"200\" src=\"https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Commerce-300x200.jpg\" class=\"image wp-image-194  attachment-medium size-medium\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto;\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Commerce-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Commerce-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Commerce-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Commerce-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Commerce-830x554.jpg 830w, https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Commerce-230x153.jpg 230w, https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Commerce-350x234.jpg 350w, https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Commerce-480x320.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/><\/a><\/div><\/div><\/div><div id=\"pgc-33-10-1\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\" ><div id=\"panel-33-10-1-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_text panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"18\" ><div style=\"text-align: left;\" data-title-color=\"#443f3f\" data-headings-color=\"#443f3f\" class=\"panel-widget-style panel-widget-style-for-33-10-1-0\" >\t\t\t<div class=\"textwidget\"><p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>Our highly experienced team of 10 commercial\/logistic is working continuously to arrange all the documents required from receiving an order from the client to shipping the final goods. We have our own logistics to support a smooth transportation of raw material and shipping goods to ports.<\/p>\n<p>We are well experienced in shipping mode such as sea and air. We work on FOB\/CIF\/FCA\/DDP. Our terms of payments are LC and TT.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>At JDK Group, we bridge the world with Bangladesh. Since 2009 we have been working in the RMG industry catering for our many valued customers with efficiency, honesty and reliability.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":2,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"page-templates\/page_fullwidth.php","meta":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/33"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=33"}],"version-history":[{"count":125,"href":"https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/33\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":754,"href":"https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/33\/revisions\/754"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.jdkfashion.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=33"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}